    <string id="str_culture_description.empire_s" text="The Hyderabadis command the Deccan plateau of the south, where the Nizam governs a patchwork of warlike domains in the fading shadow of imperial authority. Masters of fortress warfare and of playing rival powers against one another, they hold a hard, proud country of basalt hills, diamond mines and ancient citadels." />
